Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been beaten! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Red Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Do something about these handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying but... Damn, I can't break them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! He can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the guy who uncuffed Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make the key! Uncuff him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right! Bring him here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this war going to end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for hurting Ace!\NHave you learned your lesson, Red Hound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Is he a monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you let\Nyour guard down, Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you interrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just delaying the inevitable, Jinbe!\NSince you were once a Warlord,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you know what I'm capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll happily risk my life to buy some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been ready to die from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Marco! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thank you for helping me! I almost got killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.06,0:09:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the crap and uncuff me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,V-Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Are you losing your mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You better keep holding me down\Nlike that, Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you don't, I will kill Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.17,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I need to execute a traitor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you guys are Haki users?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we mess up this badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.67,0:10:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive myself for what happened today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that it's too late to save Fire Fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace, you need to get treated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you pushed yourself that far but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...I couldn't make it all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Please help Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey somebody! Help Ace! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! This way! Give him first aid now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.84,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Straw-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and treat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me see the wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Hurry up and help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Just do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you a doctor?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My organs have been burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hold out any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell that my life is ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Iva-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Inject that stuff into Ace! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you did to me, why can't you help Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I beg you! Please! Help! Help Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please inject that into Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:15.51,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Straw-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:21.55,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Ace-boy... can't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you'd never die...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hold out any longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you'd never die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...no matter what, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I even deserve to have been born?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Gold Roger had a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I know what'd happen to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.82,0:15:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd get his head cut off for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm not content if we kill him that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we prick him with a needle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,one time for every grudge\Nthat someone holds against Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Instead, we should burn him alive first
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and humiliate him in front of the whole world before he dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then everybody'll say "serves him right!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His last words should be:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm sorry I was born! I'm just a piece of trash!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think that he ever had a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wanted me to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace! You caused trouble in the city again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making a fuss about it!\NDon't give us a hard time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening, Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were stronger, I would have killed all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even have the will to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...if it weren't for Sabo\Nand an unruly little brother like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. If you see Dadan someday,\Nsay hello for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,While facing my own death,\NI even miss a woman like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, don't say that you're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing that makes me wanna stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my desire to see you fulfill your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure that you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...and live as we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Freer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Like we promised that day, I have no regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! Don't lie to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me\Nthat what I truly wanted was not fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I deserve to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wanted was the answer for that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You better tell me that my beloved son is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna save you even if it means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Rescue Ace and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...destroy the Navy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get Ace back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't speak loud enough anymore\Nfor everybody to hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.18,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...what I'm about to say now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...for loving such a good-for-nothing like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...who carries such despicable blood in his veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...up to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I deserved to be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll see as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a reality difficult to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace's death cruelly unfolds before Luffy's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But the battle does not pause.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As the pursuit intensifies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard's rage shakes all of Marineford!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.07,0:23:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Navy Headquarters Falls! Whitebeard's Unspeakable Wrath!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
